{"title_page": "Operation Java", "text_new": "{{short description|Upcoming film by Tharun Moorthy}}\n\n{{Infobox film\n| name           = Operation Java\n| image          = OperationJavaGroup.jpg\n| alt            = <!-- see WP:ALT -->\n| caption        = \n| director       = [[Tharun Moorthy]]\n| producer       = [[V Cinemas]]\n| writer         = [[Tharun Moorthy]]\n| starring       = {{Plainlist|\n*[[Balu Varghese]]\n*Lukman\n*[[Vinayakan]]\n*[[Shine Tom Chacko]]\n}}\n| music          = [[Jakes Bejoy]]\n| cinematography = [[Faiz Siddik]]\n| editing        = [[Nishad Yusuf]]\n| studio         = [[V Cinemas]]\n| country        = India\n| language       = Malayalam\n| budget         = <!-- Add with a Reliable source -->\n}}\n\n'''''Operation Java''''' is an upcoming Indian [[Malayalam language|Malayalam]]-language [[Thriller film|thriller]] movie written and directed by [[Tharun Moorthy]] as his debut film, which stars [[Vinayakan]], [[Balu Varghese]], Lukman and [[Shine Tom Chacko]]. The movie is produced by V Cinemas after [[Oru Kuprasidha Payyan]]. The film has music composed by [[Jakes Bejoy]] and cinematography done by [[Faiz Siddik]]. Sound design is done by Vishnu Govind and Sreeshankar ( Sound Factor ) .\n\n== Cast ==\n{{colbegin}}\n* [[Balu Varghese]]\n* Lukman\n* [[Vinayakan]] \n* [[Shine Tom Chacko]] \n* [[Mamtha Baiju]]  \n* [[Irshad (actor)|Irshad]]\n* [[Binu Pappu]]\n* [[Alexander Prasanth]]\n* [[Dhanya Ananya]]\n* [[Mathew Thomas]]\n* [[Binu Pappu]]\n* [[Johny Antony]]\n* [[Vinitha Koshy]]{{colend}}\n\n== Production ==\n\nOperation Java started the pre-production works on December and they released the first look poster<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.southlive.in/movie/film-news/operation-java-check-out-the-first-look-poster/|title=\u0d05\u0d31\u0d3f\u0d2f\u0d2a\u0d4d\u0d2a\u0d46\u0d1f\u0d3e\u0d24\u0d4d\u0d24 \u0d35\u0d40\u0d30\u0d28\u0d4d\u0d2e\u0d3e\u0d30\u0d41\u0d1f\u0d46 \u0d15\u0d25\u0d15\u0d33\u0d41\u0d2e\u0d3e\u0d2f\u0d3f \u0d13\u0d2a\u0d4d\u0d2